      <title>沙特王子向 CNBC 表示，OPEC+ 推迟实施意味着 2025 年初将进入低迷期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/opec-delay-reflects-early-2025-lull-saudi-prince-tells-cnbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯能源部长表示，OPEC+决定推迟恢复石油生产是为了抵消明年初季节性需求低迷的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/opec-delay-reflects-early-2025-lull-saudi-prince-tells-cnbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 13:07:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称欧洲央行将对部分银行进行 SRT 买家杠杆率测试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/ecb-is-said-to-quiz-some-banks-about-srt-buyers-use-of-leverage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行正在寻求弄清投资者如何利用借入的资金购买重大风险转移产品，以试图确保这种日益流行的结构有助于缓解风险敞口，而不是将其转移到整个银行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/ecb-is-said-to-quiz-some-banks-about-srt-buyers-use-of-leverage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 12:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国金融监督院称“增值”政策将经受住政治动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/korea-s-fss-chief-says-value-up-to-survive-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最高金融监管机构表示，由于韩国改善公司治理和提高股东回报的努力得到了两党的支持，这一举措将在政治动荡中得以延续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/korea-s-fss-chief-says-value-up-to-survive-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 08:15:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗集团因澳大利亚贸易失误损失逾 4,500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/citigroup-losses-reach-a-70-million-on-goodman-trade-afr-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，花旗集团因澳大利亚的一笔交易失误而蒙受的损失跃升至 7,000 多万澳元（4,500 万美元），这是近年来亚洲最大的大宗交易失误之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/citigroup-losses-reach-a-70-million-on-goodman-trade-afr-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
