      <title>联合健康保险公司枪击案引发健康保险公司的敌意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/unitedhealthcare-ceo-shooting-dredges-up-hatred-of-health-insurers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合健康集团公司高管布莱恩·汤普森遭枪杀事件激起了美国人的强烈愤怒，他们认为医疗保险行业经常无法支付高额医疗费用并阻碍了人们获得必要的治疗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/unitedhealthcare-ceo-shooting-dredges-up-hatred-of-health-insurers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 23:23:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
